Fixpaper
--------

== Usage ==

Command-line:
   ./fixpaper [input image filename]

== Interface ==

Left Panel: The uncropped image, black & white with contrast auto-enhanced.
Green Lines: The cropping area
Right Panel: Same as the left, but cropped.

== Controls ==

Left click: Drag 1 corner of the cropping area
Right click: Drag all corners of the cropping area
     1: drag corner 1
     2: drag corner 2
W or 3: drag corner 3
Q or 4: drag corner 4
< or >: rotate 90 degrees
Backspace: Reset the cropping area

Enter: save
ESC: quit